37 #include <ros/ros.h>
38 #include <string>
39 
40 #include <moveit/benchmarks/BenchmarkOptions.h>
41 #include <moveit/benchmarks/BenchmarkExecutor.h>
42 
43 int main(int argc, char** argv)
44 {
45  ros::init(argc, argv, "moveit_run_benchmark");
46  ros::AsyncSpinner spinner(1);
47  spinner.start();
48 
49  // Read benchmark options from param server
50  moveit_ros_benchmarks::BenchmarkOptions opts(ros::this_node::getName());
51  // Setup benchmark server
52  moveit_ros_benchmarks::BenchmarkExecutor server;
53 
54  std::vector<std::string> planning_pipelines;
55  opts.getPlanningPipelineNames(planning_pipelines);
56  server.initialize(planning_pipelines);
57 
58  // Running benchmarks
59  if (!server.runBenchmarks(opts))
60  ROS_ERROR("Failed to run all benchmarks");
61 }
